I couldn't do jack for her.


514
0:44:26,945 --> 0:44:28,865
- Hey.
- Don't touch me!


515
0:44:28,865 --> 0:44:34,65
- ( Sobbing )
- Hey.


516
0:44:34,65 --> 0:44:36,824
You okay?


517
0:44:36,824 --> 0:44:40,984
I saw her.


518
0:44:40,984 --> 0:44:44,223
I saw her
through your eyes.


519
0:44:44,223 --> 0:44:46,303
You stayed with her
the whole time.


520
0:44:46,303 --> 0:44:51,622
Yeah, well, you got to
understand something, all right?


521
0:44:51,622 --> 0:44:56,222
I was hoping
she'd come out of it, you know.


522
0:44:56,222 --> 0:44:59,101
Give me something
I could work with.


523
0:44:59,101 --> 0:45:1,301
Yeah.


524
0:45:1,301 --> 0:45:3,701
Look, I--


525
0:45:3,701 --> 0:45:6,18
Why didn't you do
something about it?


526
0:45:6,18 --> 0:45:9,46
