my nose where it wasn't wanted.


530
0:45:22,418 --> 0:45:24,378
This your wife?


531
0:45:24,378 --> 0:45:30,457
Yeah, we, uh-- Well, not anymore,
we're getting a divorce.


532
0:45:30,457 --> 0:45:33,337
It's funny.


533
0:45:33,337 --> 0:45:37,256
Little things used to mean
so much to Shelly.


534
0:45:37,256 --> 0:45:40,696
I used to think
they were kind of trivial.


535
0:45:40,696 --> 0:45:52,814
Believe me,
nothing is trivial.


536
0:45:52,814 --> 0:46:1,573
You shouldn't smoke these.
They'll kill you.


537
0:46:1,573 --> 0:46:8,132
You going to vanish
into thin air again?


538
0:46:8,132 --> 0:46:13,651
I thought I'd use
your front door.


539
0:46:13,651 --> 0:46:20,73
