your sister? ( Laughing )


564
0:47:45,879 --> 0:47:49,158
My father's daughter.
That's right.


565
0:47:49,158 --> 0:47:52,278
What's the matter,
you don't see the resemblance?


566
0:47:52,278 --> 0:47:54,518
Now, let's take it
from the top, friend.


567
0:47:54,518 --> 0:47:57,997
With a lot of detail.
What do you say?


568
0:47:57,997 --> 0:48:1,397
He had a bird with him.
Nearly pecked my face off.


569
0:48:1,397 --> 0:48:4,716
He told me to tell T-bird
that death was on its way.


570
0:48:4,716 --> 0:48:6,916
Whatever the fuck that means.


571
0:48:6,916 --> 0:48:11,595
Draven. He said his name
was Eric Draven.


572
0:48:11,595 --> 0:48:13,635
Want to relax
that thing now?


573
0:48:13,635 --> 0:48:18,194
This bird man, he just happened
to let you live, huh?


574
0:48:18,194 --> 0:48:22,434
You sure you ain't making all this up
just to save your own ass?


575
0:48:22,434 --> 0:48:25,114
I ain't making all this up.


576
0:48:25,114 --> 0:48:31,153
I ain't twisted
like you two fucks.


577
0:48:31,153 --> 0:48:37,672
All right.


578
0:48:37,672 --> 0:48:42,551
A boy and his bird.
Awful touching.


579
0:48:42,551 --> 0:48:52,31
Yeah. ( Laughing )


580
0:48:52,31 --> 0:49:1,829
For fuck's sake, die, will ya?
Give me that thing.


581
0:49:1,829 --> 0:49:4,108
Thanks.


582
0:49:4,108 --> 0:49:6,388
Funboy said he saw
a black bird too.


583
0:49:6,388 --> 0:49:8,948
A big one.


584
0:49:8,948 --> 0:49:13,707
Then he choked to death
on his own blood.


585
0:49:13,707 --> 0:49:21,706
I'll have the janitor
come on up.


586
0:49:21,706 --> 0:49:23,866
( Purring )


587
0:49:23,866 --> 0:49:39,584
** ( Electric Guitar )


588
0:49:39,584 --> 0:50:11,259
