599
0:50:52,654 --> 0:50:54,734
Tin Tin was a dick.


600
0:50:54,734 --> 0:50:57,653
Tin Tin.
Sheesh.


601
0:50:57,653 --> 0:51:1,773
Fire it up! Fire it up!
Fire it up! Fire it up!


602
0:51:1,773 --> 0:51:6,92
Fire it up!


603
0:51:6,92 --> 0:51:8,172
No Funboy.


604
0:51:8,172 --> 0:51:12,11
Probably still...
