620
0:52:25,201 --> 0:52:29,81
Stupid asshair!
You hit my car!


621
0:52:29,81 --> 0:52:35,72
( Groaning )


622
0:52:35,72 --> 0:52:41,519
What do you want, man?
Money? Drugs? I got it.


623
0:52:41,519 --> 0:52:44,359
We could use you.
You did Tin Tin.


624
0:52:44,359 --> 0:52:50,158
- This is business, right?
- ( Gun Cocks ) Faster.


625
0:52:50,158 --> 0:52:54,238
You got that cream stuff?


626
0:52:54,238 --> 0:52:58,77
I hate this.
