This ain't good.


644
0:54:19,666 --> 0:54:23,66
T-bird!
I got you, man!


645
0:54:23,66 --> 0:54:28,985
- Shit!
- ( Screaming )


646
0:54:28,985 --> 0:54:38,184
( Groaning, Car Door Chiming )


647
0:54:38,184 --> 0:54:40,463
( T-bird ) Remember?
Yeah, I remember everything.


648
0:54:40,463 --> 0:54:43,623
But I don't know what--
What? Huh? What?


649
0:54:43,623 --> 0:54:46,343
What are you talking about?
No, no, no, no, no.


650
0:54:46,343 --> 0:54:49,382
You mean that place downtown?
Yeah, I remember her.


651
0:54:49,382 --> 0:54:51,542
We needed to put some fear
into that little lady.


652
0:54:51,542 --> 0:54:54,741
She wasn't going along
with our tenant relocation program.


653
0:54:54,741 --> 0:54:58,261
And her idiot boyfriend shows up
and turns a simple sweep-and-clear...


654
0:54:58,261 --> 0:55:1,62
into a total cluster fuck!
Who gives a shit?


655
0:55:1,62 --> 0:55:4,82
It's ancient history!
Why? What do you want?


656
0:55:4,82 --> 0:55:11,59
What is it? What?
Speak to me. Speak!


657
0:55:11,59 --> 0:55:14,499
Did you send us
these complaints?


658
0:55:14,499 --> 0:55:17,738
Come here!
"Abashed the devil stood."


659
0:55:17,738 --> 0:55:20,98
Does it get you sweaty?


660
0:55:20,98 --> 0:55:25,137
I know you. I know you.
I knew I knew you.


661
0:55:25,137 --> 0:55:29,217
I knew I knew you.
But you ain't you.


662
0:55:29,217 --> 0:55:33,56
You can't be you. We put you through
the window. There ain't no coming back.


663
0:55:33,56 --> 0:55:36,416
This is the really real world.
There ain't no coming back.


664
0:55:36,416 --> 0:55:38,775
We killed you dead.
There ain't no coming back.


665
0:55:38,775 --> 0:55:43,135
( Grunting, Muttering )
T-bird--


666
0:55:43,135 --> 0:55:48,414
There ain't no coming back!
There ain't no coming back!


667
0:55:48,414 --> 0:55:52,494
- T-bird.
- ( T-bird Panting )


668
0:55:52,494 --> 0:55:55,773
- ( Engine Revs )
- "Abashed the devil stood...


669
0:55:55,773 --> 0:55:58,693
