670
0:55:58,693 --> 0:56:6,12
"And felt how awful goodness is."


671
0:56:6,12 --> 0:56:14,931
( Tires Squealing )


672
0:56:14,931 --> 0:56:44,7
( Gasping )
T-bird. T-bird.


673
0:56:44,7 --> 0:57:5,724
( Crow Caws )


674
0:57:5,724 --> 0:57:8,4
