Black coffee and cigarettes?


685
0:57:48,838 --> 0:57:52,78
So what did you take
to become mother of the year?


686
0:57:52,78 --> 0:57:57,37
Oh, it wasn't drugs.
Someone kind of woke me up.


687
0:57:57,37 --> 0:58:2,636
- Who?
- Oh, it was nuts.


688
0:58:2,636 --> 0:58:10,75
You're acting weird. Did you win
the lottery or something, Darla?


689
0:58:10,75 --> 0:58:14,275
Oh, forget it. I never was
too good at this mommy shit.


690
0:58:14,275 --> 0:58:18,394
Over easy.


691
0:58:18,394 --> 0:58:33,72
I like 'em
over easy... Mom.


692
0:58:33,72 --> 0:58:35,312
Hey, Albrecht.


693
0:58:35,312 --> 0:58:37,872
( Sighs )


694
0:58:37,872 --> 0:58:40,751
This is the third hit
in your hood in 24 hours.


695
0:58:40,751 --> 0:58:43,951
We just fished this out of the river.
He's fused to his own car.


696
0:58:43,951 --> 0:58:48,7
- We're gonna have to l.D. his teeth.
- His name is T-bird.


697
0:58:48,7 --> 0:58:49,99
Arson was his specialty.


698
0:58:49,99 --> 0:58:51,95
Looks like he zigged
when he should have zagged.


699
0:58:51,95 --> 0:58:55,789
- Case closed.
- Bull-fuckin'-shit.


700
0:58:55,789 --> 0:59:1,548
Come here.


701
0:59:1,548 --> 0:59:3,508
You're holding out on me.


702
0:59:3,508 --> 0:59:6,988
I got a goddamn vigilante killer
knocking off scumbags left and right...


703
0:59:6,988 --> 0:59:10,187
and you're covering up
for somebody.


704
0:59:10,187 --> 0:59:12,587
Who's the cartoon character
in the painted face?


705
0:59:12,587 --> 0:59:16,386
- You're the detective. You tell me.
