just a fucking automobile accident?


710
0:59:26,145 --> 0:59:28,425
- Come on!
- Yeah. Good speech though.


711
0:59:28,425 --> 0:59:30,424
I didn't want to interrupt you.
It sounded good.


712
0:59:30,424 --> 0:59:32,384
You gotta write that shit down.


713
0:59:32,384 --> 0:59:34,304
All right, smart-ass.


714
0:59:34,304 --> 0:59:37,304
The captain's got a little
love note waiting for you.


715
0:59:37,304 --> 0:59:41,143
- Welcome to the first day
of the rest of your suspension.
- Suspension?


716
0:59:41,143 --> 0:59:44,823
- For what?
- Misconduct.


717
0:59:44,823 --> 0:59:48,742
( Dials Phone )
